{"tid":1572621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"背包被搜出餐刀　浸大新聞網記者被警方帶走","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T18:40:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d907b001b60d5b394f13609cc9fe9100b544a9dc","tid":1572621,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1480743_1_L_20190916010625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1480743_1_L_20190916010625.jpg&h=bce9ee09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸大廣播新聞網表示，他們有記者昨晚於英皇道與炮台山道交界，被警方截停檢查記者證和身份證，並搜查背包，期間其中一名記者被搜出一把餐刀，該名記者指日前為慶祝中秋，用作切月餅，記者最終被警員帶上私家車。<br />\n<br />\n在搜背包期間，警員以私隱理由阻止新聞網記者拍攝搜袋過程，並用盾牌阻擋鏡頭，浸大廣播新聞網譴責警方無理濫捕，促請警方盡快釋放有關記者。<br />\n<br />\n浸大有講師到北角警署了解情況，並已聯絡律師。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480743-20190916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480743-20190916.htm&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=f8aca578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480743-20190916.htm&h=3179ac9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480743-20190916.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b8e608723d2aa95ba154cfaff2970c83b572f13a","tid":1572621,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:20:57.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"926743f3850d1f61cc27c75f086a0061e3d29a4f","tid":1572621,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"78f4a1644ae9ba6e742a0e7f90bf4e147aeafe09","tid":1572621,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019